Root Beer is a 13-year-old male Lab/Weimaraner, 85 lbs, mix who has a serious zest for life. Don&#39;t let his age fool you &mdash; this distinguished gentleman has the heart of an explorer and the spirit of a loyal companion. His favorite pastimes?&nbsp;Car rides, leisurely walks, human attention, and&hellip; relocating his dog food bowl around the house. (Yes, it&rsquo;s his version of interior design.)

Whether he&#39;s trotting alongside you on a trail or cozying up for some head scratches, Root Beer knows how to make the most of every moment &mdash; and he wants to share them all with you.&nbsp;

&nbsp;

