Gunnie is a 13-year-old female Lab-Weimaraner mix with a heart as big as her soulful eyes. This sweet, silver-coated lady is in her golden years, but don&rsquo;t let her age fool you &mdash; she still perks up for her favorite things: leisurely walks, windows-down car rides, tasty treats, and just about any kind of affection you&rsquo;re offering.

At around 75 lbs, Gunnie is the perfect size for snuggling beside you on the couch or accompanying you on a short stroll through the neighborhood. She&#39;s friendly with humans of all kinds and would thrive in a calm home where she can soak up love and enjoy her well-earned retirement.

Gunnie is fully vetted, spayed, and house-trained. She does well with other mellow dogs and would be happy as either a solo companion or with her brother Root Beer. She doesn&rsquo;t ask for much &mdash; just your time, your kindness, and a soft bed to call her own.




